    put:
      responses:
        default:
          description: default
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
                example: ""
      summary: Account Change Password
      operationId: Account_Change_Password
      description: "Change password or SSH key of an account and propagate changes on
        the target host.  If the body is empty, an automatic password change is
        performed: the password or the SSH key are changed to a newly generated
        value, according to the password change policy on the domain.  Note: the
        password change must be enabled on the domain, with a plugin that will
        be used to change the password on the target host."

          name: account_id
          description: Generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - in: path
          name: credential_type

          required: true
          schema:
            type: string

            {
                "password": "${password}"

          description: Header generated by shuffler.io OpenAPI
          required: false
          example: application/json
          schema:
            type: string
